title: InfusionTea
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Catering
description: A modern tea house cafe located in the College Park area. Features an extensive organic tea menu in addition to vegetarian and vegan fare. Serving breakfast items, sandwiches and wraps, appetizers, soups, pizza, and salads. The space is available for hosting garden tea party, bridal showers, birthday parties, and special dinner events.
